title: Night Love
description: The old bookshop smells of leather and dust, with narrow aisles filled to the brim with yellowed paperbacks and ancient hardcovers. A lone cat naps on a stack of vintage magazines by the counter, its tail twitching in its sleep. The dim light from a stained-glass window casts soft patterns on the wooden floor.
